#sms_service client
to run dev server:
- install virtualenv > 'pip install virtualenv'
- choose a folder, create virtual environment > 'virtualenv venv'
- download repository 'venv' folder content to the 'venv' folder created
- activate virtual environment> 'source bin/activate'
- install dependencies > 'pip install --upgrade -r requirements.txt'
- configure 'config.cfg' file with appropriate IPs
- run flask with 'flask run -h <your_ip>'
- go to '<your_ip>/5000/sms_service' in your browser